DONNY:
No! Stop! No!

275
00:08:54,117 --> 00:08:56,536
[ Why-wolves snarling, housies screaming ]

276
00:08:56,619 --> 00:08:58,705
Now, go be a jerk to those Why-wolves.

277
00:08:58,788 --> 00:08:59,581
No.

278
00:08:59,664 --> 00:09:00,498
[ snarling, screaming continue ]

279
00:09:03,001 --> 00:09:05,628
I'll use my musical messages
to stop them.

280
00:09:05,712 --> 00:09:06,546
Let's see.

281
00:09:06,629 --> 00:09:09,424
I've got one on the ethics
of laundry, "Crosswalkery."

282
00:09:09,507 --> 00:09:10,759
Ooh, here's a good one.

283
00:09:10,842 --> 00:09:12,218
[ screaming continues ]

284
00:09:12,302 --> 00:09:14,929
Man, the town is getting creamed!

285
00:09:15,013 --> 00:09:17,932
By not being a jerk,
you're being a real jerk, Donny.

286
00:09:18,016 --> 00:09:19,100
» Comb your hair right

287
00:09:19,184 --> 00:09:20,435
J It's a good time

288
00:09:20,518 --> 00:09:21,603
J Sticky, sticky pomade »

289
00:09:21,686 --> 00:09:22,937
5 Short back and sides

290
00:09:23,021 --> 00:09:24,272
[ screaming continues ]

291
00:09:24,355 --> 00:09:27,525
Why isn't anyone paying attention to my words?

292
00:09:27,609 --> 00:09:29,319
He sure is sensitive about his songs.

293
00:09:29,402 --> 00:09:30,236
[ gasps ]

294
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,697
It's 'cause they think your songs are dumb!

295
00:09:32,781 --> 00:09:33,615
Wha?

296
00:09:33,698 --> 00:09:34,866
What are you saying?

297
00:09:34,949 --> 00:09:37,202
If we don't encourage his talent,
he might revert back

298
00:09:37,285 --> 00:09:39,579
to jerk Don--
oh, oh!

299
00:09:39,662 --> 00:09:43,374
Hey, Donny, everyone says
your songs are super balls.

300
00:09:43,458 --> 00:09:46,169
They all think you're a real jerk!

301
00:09:46,252 --> 00:09:48,338
But --
but I've changed!

302
00:09:48,421 --> 00:09:50,340
Why would they say that?

303
00:09:50,423 --> 00:09:52,175
» Empathy, empathy J»

304
00:09:52,258 --> 00:09:53,343
J» Put your mind inside -- J

305
00:09:53,426 --> 00:09:55,845
[ laughter ]

306
00:09:55,929 --> 00:09:58,389
You are so pathetic...

307
00:09:58,473 --> 00:10:00,391
so comical.

308
00:10:00,475 --> 00:10:02,769
[ laughs ]

309
00:10:02,852 --> 00:10:03,686
[ growling ]

310
00:10:05,855 --> 00:10:08,108
Think I'm a jerk, do they?

311
00:10:08,191 --> 00:10:11,611
I'm feeling...obnoxious!

312
00:10:11,694 --> 00:10:13,947
[ roars ]

313
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:16,199
You wolves are cool!

314
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:17,826
Just kidding!

315
00:10:17,909 --> 00:10:18,993
[ laughs ]

316
00:10:19,077 --> 00:10:20,662
Obnoxygen cloud!

317
00:10:20,745 --> 00:10:21,663
Egress!

318
00:10:21,746 --> 00:10:23,832
[ Why-wolves whimpering ]

319
00:10:23,915 --> 00:10:25,667
[ breathes heavily ]

320
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:29,838
ALL:
The town is saved! Yay!

321
00:10:29,921 --> 00:10:31,005
Get off of me, nerds!

322
00:10:31,089 --> 00:10:32,465
You did it, Donny.

323
00:10:32,549 --> 00:10:34,134
You're a full-blown jerk again.

324
00:10:34,217 --> 00:10:36,136
What?!
You're the jerk!

325
00:10:36,219 --> 00:10:38,930
Housies, ready to hear my new song?

326
00:10:39,013 --> 00:10:43,268
It's about how Finn will betray
you just to save lives.

327
00:10:43,351 --> 00:10:44,936
I'm sorry, Donny.

328
00:10:45,019 --> 00:10:47,605
I'll never forgive you, Finn!

329
00:10:47,689 --> 00:10:48,481
[ roaring ]

330
00:10:52,026 --> 00:10:52,986
Come on.

331
00:10:53,069 --> 00:10:55,238
We can go stare wistfully at the lake.

332
00:10:55,321 --> 00:10:58,283
I'd --
I'd like that very much.

333
00:10:58,366 --> 00:11:00,702
[ indistinct shouting ]

334
00:11:02,745 --> 00:11:05,832
Hey! | love being a jerk!

335
00:11:05,915 --> 00:11:08,459
Thanks, Finn.
Finn?

336
00:11:08,543 --> 00:11:10,003
Finn, you loser.

337
00:11:10,086 --> 00:11:11,296
[ sniffles ]

338
00:11:11,671 --> 00:11:14,674
I'll never... forget you.

339
00:11:20,096 --> 00:11:23,808
» Come along with me »

340
00:11:23,892 --> 00:11:27,770
2 And the butterflies and bees

341
00:11:27,854 --> 00:11:31,774
» We can wander through the forest J»

342
00:11:31,858 --> 00:11:35,737
> And do so as we please >

343
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:39,741
» Come along with me »

344
00:11:39,824 --> 00:11:42,493
D To a cliff under a tree »

